{"tid":733070,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"部腦係咁不定時黑畫面自動 reboot求教","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T12:52:20.000Z","uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"972fc5ccb134061c28a688ffe013f59a423c2b53","tid":733070,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"想問下咁多位巴打，最近部機係咁毫無徵兆咁自動 boot機，冇 BSOD，就咁眼前一黑（已 disable windows個 auto restart），唔知係咪 display/ power supply死，買新 parts之前想請教下驚買錯野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- 開頭係打機 set高畫質會出現，後來試下用 set低 d好似好 d，但結果都同樣發生，到而家試過好幾次 log in完一禁左下角 windows就又 reboot<br />\n<br />\n- RAM用緊 8gb x2，試過輪流抆左其中一條，結果都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n- 用 safe mode照樣係咁<br />\n<br />\n-用過 windows個 memory diagnosis話 no error found<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以指教下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c842dedaa5278f621d6d52fac34bb660abe6a9a","tid":733070,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"聽bi bi聲"},{"pid":"e0e135586675a6bbc74eaf975884e4081953c0df","tid":733070,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c842dedaa5278f621d6d52fac34bb660abe6a9a","tid":733070,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"聽bi bi聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以詳細少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又冇 bibi聲，純屬係好似平時開機咁"},{"pid":"917b703627129a84275cce106b6bfa3fbc803e4b","tid":733070,"uid":101490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"power死<br />\n應該係你display熱到要着風扇就斷"},{"pid":"811cfa0378a4e